s one donor, and incorporation of one atom of oxygen\"),\n    },\n    \"GO:0018570\": {\n        \"is_a\": (\"is_a: GO:0016702 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on single donors with incorporation of molecular oxygen, incorporation of two atoms of oxygen\", \"is_a: GO:0016708 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen, NAD(P)H as one donor, and incorporation of two atoms of oxygen into one donor\"),\n    },\n}\n\nTRACKER = 'property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31969\" xsd:anyURI\\n'\n\nfor fpath in glob.glob(\"terms/GO_*.obo\"):\n    with open(fpath) as fh:\n        content = fh.read()\n    lines = content.splitlines(keepends=True)\n    # Extract GO ID from id line\n    go_id = None\n    for line in lines:\n        if line.startswith(\"id: \"):\n            go_id = line.strip().split(\" \")[1]\n            break\n    if go_id is None or go_id not in changes:\n        continue\n    term_changes = changes[go_id]\n    modified = False\n    for key, (old, new) in term_changes.items():\n        if old in content:\n            content = content.replace(old, new, 1)\n            modified = True\n        else:\n            print(f\"WARNING: could not find {key} pattern for {go_id} in {fpath}\")\n    # Add tracker item if not present\n    if 'github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31969' not in content:\n        # insert before the last blank line(s)\n        # content ends with newline; we can just append before final newline\n        # OBO stanza ends with a blank line; for a single stanza file, we want to add before the trailing blank line.\n        # If the file ends with \\n\\n, add before last \\n.\n        if content.endswith('\\n\\n'):\n            content = content[:-1] + TRACKER + '\\n'\n        elif content.endswith('\\n'):\n            content = content[:-1] + TRACKER + '\\n'\n        else:\n            content = content + '\\n' + TRACKER\n        modified = True\n    if modified:\n        with open(fpath, \"w\") as fh:\n            fh.write(content)\n        print(f\"Updated {go_id}\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"No changes for {go_id}\")\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/terms/apply_changes.py","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"terms/apply_changes.py","time":{"start":1778468485344,"end":1778468485352}},"id":"prt_e14faba37001h1SNsqqY3Z2g9n","sessionID":"ses_1eb0a0addffeb4H5wZOwTgWV2C","messageID":"msg_e14fa91ae0013IFi4PhOmtbS7s"}}
